{"tid":909841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（資料整合）唔係個個大陸藝人有share中國一點也不能少","createTime":"2018-11-20T16:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T18:55:43.000Z","uid":157483,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8d505ae82ad4146eea703350aa68f140d90d2e92","tid":909841,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"特登睇左好多人微博<br />\n大陸方面：薛之謙、丁噹、jony j都冇share到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣我up得出名既都冇人share，唯一一個楊丞琳都澄清左唔係佢本人轉發<br />\n香港方面就大把賤人囉 包括：陳偉霆 陳小春 應采兒 王嘉爾 劉愷威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時未失守既包括gem 王祖藍 陳奕迅等等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88bac51f80f318c7be9e818dfe3789b9869193e7","tid":909841,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"清泉 vs人渣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd354f06f504da5c77c14e80e02a836fbf2e782","tid":909841,"uid":200328,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-20T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特登睇左好多人微博<br />\n大陸方面：薛之謙、丁噹、jony j都冇share到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣我up得出名既都冇人share，唯一一個楊丞琳都澄清左唔係佢本人轉發<br />\n香港方面就大把賤人囉 包括：<span style=\"color: red;\">陳偉霆 陳小春 應采兒 王嘉爾 劉愷威</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n暫時未失守既包括gem 王祖藍 陳奕迅等等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢班香港方面有係香港出沒既咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n變晒大陸方面啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而gem果班雖然俾連登仔插得勁, 但仍然會出現係香港, 今次仲無share到, 算係揦返拃沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9bcbe6ba284873556a6e0c252f1946eea23a97","tid":909841,"uid":5077,"like":7,"dislik